                      java.lang.String localServerName,

               throws java.io.IOException
        Method that lists the details given site.
        format of each output: site_name , local_server_name, storage_server(IP or hostname), date/time of last backup

        root - Tbe web_backups folder path

        siteName - The site name To be listed
